{
  "stem": "24364.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even the shorter distance to Cyprus proved too long for the little coal that was there, so they started really stripping the ship.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took all the beds, all the mats, every piece of wood which was not absolutely necessary, and heated the ship with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ship was floating on the water just like a metal skeleton.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was really the only time we were frightened, because any time a storm could happen and we would have been done for.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Incidentally, I remember one time prior to that that I was so desperate because of the way we-- we were sleeping and couldn't really breathe well.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I decided-- even though the weather was really bad, I decided to go on deck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since the weather was very bad, there were very few people on deck, so I found a place to lay down, which was great.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I fell asleep, only to be awakened by the worst storm I have ever experienced.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It-- it was pouring rain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I can only remember when I opened my eyes, the ship was going from side to side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The mast was going like this and like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I got desperately seasick, but really desperately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I couldn't move and the rain was pouring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was lying there, just-- I thought, I'll-- I'll never survive this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I think after an hour or two somebody from the Haganah who had come up deck to look around-- because I think I was the only one there-- whether somebody was there found me and dragged me down.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I don't remember what happened after that, but that was one of the worst experiences of my life.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
